//
// Pillars
// -------
// âœ… Efficiency    â€“ hot-path indexes (slug, (courseId, order), (userId, moduleId), etc.)
// âœ… Robustness    â€“ explicit relations w/ `onDelete` where it helps data hygiene
// âœ… Simplicity    â€“ JSON questions, simple progress models, single `expiresAt`
// âœ… Ease of mgmt  â€“ clear comments + obvious schema
// âœ… Security      â€“ no extra PII; auth models as expected
//
